---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Myself" sideBarActiveItemID="myself">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Myself</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="mb-4">
      TL;DR: I'm just a human being, like every other one of our Mother Earth,
      which means I'm unique in my own ways and grateful for the opportunity to
      live day after day.
    </div>

    <div>Longer version: You can know me better below.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="mb-2 text-2xl w-full font-bold">👤 My identity</div>
    <div class="mb-2">I am...</div>
    <ul class="list-disc mx-6 grid">
      <li>named Tiago Romero</li>
      <li>identified by the pronouns he/him/his</li>
      <li>Amor, to my wife Cíntia</li>
      <li>Papai, to my dog Sherlock</li>
      <li>
        Aries on Sun, Leo on Rising, Sagittarius on Moon (all these Fire Zodiac
        signs🔥)
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="mb-2 text-2xl w-full font-bold">🇧🇷 My origins</div>
    <div class="mb-2">I am...</div>
    <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-5 grid">
      <li>a Paulistano (born and raised in São Paulo, SP, Brasil)</li>
      <li>an American and first-generation immigrant</li>
      <li>living in the Sacramento Area in California, USA</li>
      <li>a non-Hispanic Latino, to the Census 2020</li>
      <li>a Spanish-Italian-Brazilian by birth</li>
      <li>
        fluent in Portuguese and English, intermediate in Spanish, basic in
        French
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="mb-2 text-2xl w-full font-bold">🤸🏽 My interests</div>
    <div class="mb-2">I am...</div>
    <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-5 grid">
      <li>an ethical vegan since 1/1/2017</li>
      <li>a monthly donor to several rescued animal sanctuaries</li>
      <li>a sober, alcohol-free, drug-free, mostly medication-free</li>
      <li>a frequent blood donor at Red Cross every 2 months since 2018</li>
      <li>
        a musician: I play the guitar, ukulele, berimbau, atabaque, pandeiro,
        triângulo, agogô and recorder
      </li>
      <li>a weekend hiker</li>
      <li>a mindfulness practitioner, notably meditation and journaling</li>
      <li>
        working towards my freestanding handstands, full splits and front splits
      </li>
      <li>
        working out with jump rope, kettlebells, gymnastic rings and
        calisthenics
      </li>
      <li>planning towards my early retirement</li>
      <li>a person with 40+ tattoos</li>
      <li>homebrewing my own kombucha since 2018</li>
      <li>roasting my own coffee</li>
      <li>an absolute fan of Brazilian indie music</li>
      <li>into minimalist and barefoot shoes</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="mb-2 text-2xl w-full font-bold">⛔ My no-interests</div>
    <div class="mb-2">I am...</div>
    <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-5 grid">
      <li>not defined by my career</li>
      <li>
        not trying to become important, an influencer, the next tech celebrity,
        etc.
      </li>
      <li>not more relevant than anyone else</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
